Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Main Title 1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Main Title 2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:06.18,Italics Dialogue,News,0000,0000,0000,,Not a day goes by in Paris without someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:09.87,Italics Dialogue,News,0000,0000,0000,,mentioning the name of \NMr. Shinomiya Kojiro, the chef of SHINO'S,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:12.59,Italics Dialogue,News,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's opening his first \Nrestaurant in Japan in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:15.75,Italics Dialogue,News,0000,0000,0000,,Gourmands have mounting expectations \Nfor Mr. Shinomiya's dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:18.55,Italics Dialogue,News,0000,0000,0000,,as he is called the Magician of Legumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:19.91,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.12,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I barely get any sleep \Ngetting ready for the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:27.19,Italics Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why Chef Dojima \Nsuggested sending over a student
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.13,Italics Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,to serve as your opening staff. \NIt'd be mutually beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.88,sign_675_12_Shinomiya_Kojiro,Sign 0029,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Shinomiya Kojiro \N{\fs20} Chef, French Restaurant SHINO'S
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:35.53,Flashback Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you would be happy to cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.93,Flashback Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,given that the request is coming from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.51,Flashback Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,a sad hired chef at Totsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.17,Italics Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,So he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.48,Italics Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before, \Ndon't hold that against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:45.73,Flashback Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know about any of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:48.98,Flashback Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hired chef for the Totsuki Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:55.11,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept anyone less \Nthan one of the Autumn Election finalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:56.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:04.46,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me, Shinomiya-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.76,Episode Title,Sign 0235,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}The Magician Once More
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:40.49,Main Dialogue Top,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting you,\N of all people, Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was surprised, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.89,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd end up in your restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.15,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in Shinomiya Kojiro's kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:53.04,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I need to make a visible \Nmark if I'm gonna pass the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.57,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy, but I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.28,Main Dialogue,Shine,0000,0000,0000,,First, you'll be wrapping up \Nconstruction and interior work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.57,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's the stage they're still at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.53,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.64,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to get fired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.35,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Chef Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.33,sign_4507_36_Gao_Wei___Servic,Sign 0311,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Gao Wei \N {\fs18}Service Manager, \NSHINO'S Flagship Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.33,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,We have to create the menu \Nat the same time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.96,sign_4588_39_Lucie_Hugo___Chi,Sign 0313,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Lucie Hugo \N {\fs20}Chief Blucher, \NSHINO'S Flagship Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:12.86,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.44,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,We should ask contractors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:19.50,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Considering our remaining budget, \Nwe'll do what we can on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:23.11,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I was very selective about things \Nlike the interior and the dishware.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.04,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,But Chef Shinomiya, you could \Nget any budget you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.60,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,You have the Pluspol Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.67,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,All the sponsors who backed \Nmy flagship restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.12,sign_5021_48_Fill_in_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,500)}You're thinking about opening a new restaurant at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.12,sign_5021_49_Fill_in_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,500)}Don't go, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.12,sign_5021_50_Fill_in_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,500)}Come back in 6 months... No, a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.93,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,have opposed my opening this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.70,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask them for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.01,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh! You're too proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.15,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,The pre-open is tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:40.18,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.82,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,We're staff from SHINO'S, \Nthe flagship restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:47.45,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to support the Tokyo restaurant \Nuntil things settle down after it opens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:47.99,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.42,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:54.28,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,He's the head chef of \NSHINO'S Tokyo, Abel Blondin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:58.96,sign_5607_60_Abel_Blondin___H,Sign 0355,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Abel Blondin \N Head Chef, SHINO'S Tokyo \N{\fs20} (Ex Sous Chef, SHINO'S)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.66,Main Dialogue Top,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,He was the sous chef in the main restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.96,Main Dialogue Top,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,so he's Chef Shinomiya's right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.17,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.55,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.16,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.04,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut the chatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.68,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Opening a restaurant's tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.40,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm lucky I get to train \Nat your restaurant, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.02,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and just carry the cabinet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.02,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.61,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting so familiar with Chef Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.97,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,He has no idea how long it took me \Nto get friendly with Chef Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.95,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,And when he finally picked me to be \Nthe head chef of the Tokyo restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.81,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,it was the best moment of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.61,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.69,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,It's only the millionth time \Nyou're telling us this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:40.22,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,But Chef Shinomiya's gotten \Npretty mellow, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:42.25,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Did the change happen \Nafter he went to Japan in spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.23,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.29,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,He was some kind of judge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.72,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,I think he became a bit nicer \Nwhen he got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:51.19,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,He'll teach you with patience \Nif you ask him about cooking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.06,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.45,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,He might complain while doing it, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.91,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he actually likes teaching \Nand looking after people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.52,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on the work at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.61,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shinomiya-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.70,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,what made you decide \Nto open a new restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,And why in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.36,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I read in {\i1}Totsuki Sports{\i0} that it's rare \Nto open a new restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,when you're trying to get \Nthree Michelin stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.25,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you mean earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.14,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,About being lucky that \Nyou can train at my restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:24.16,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been easier to pass the Stagiaire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.33,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,if you'd been assigned\Nto a small local restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.30,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I need to come up with a specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.81,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay the way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.87,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take one step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.97,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and shine a new light on my cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.57,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.85,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.23,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally see the light \Nat the end of the tunnel, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.72,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.51,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make something—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.74,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.25,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.31,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Chef Shinomiya will cook for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.12,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.13,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Set the table, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.88,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get to eat \NChef Shinomiya's staff lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.00,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Mincing chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:10.26,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Carefully sauteeing mushrooms,\Nhen-of-the-woods, and shimeji with butter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:14.40,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Then pour in an appareil made from \Neggs, soy milk, and white miso
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.85,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,into a mold lined with pie crust dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.94,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is this dish called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.26,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,It's a quiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.08,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,It's originally a regional dish \Nfrom Lorraine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.49,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,and a typical lunch menu item,\N even in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:36.16,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you'd know, since you're \Nnot familiar with France.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.96,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for a staff lunch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.50,Italics Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.25,Italics Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,The magic of legumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.36,Italics Dialogue,YL,0000,0000,0000,,What is this crunchiness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.43,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Burdock root, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.64,Main Dialogue,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Bur-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.89,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.65,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredient tends to be \Navoided in the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.05,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The crunchy texture of \Nthinly-shaved burdock root
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.17,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,combines with the melty cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:13.24,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It pairs well with the juicy chicken \Nand the black pepper, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:16.99,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,How'd he achieve such deep flavors \Nwithout even using bouillon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:21.28,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,He extracted the sweetness and \Nbitterness from the skin of the burdock root
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.63,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,in perfect balance, to provide an edge to the \Nmellow flavors of the chicken and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:28.42,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Combining Japanese ingredients \Nin this way into a regional French dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.59,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,This dish is good enough to serve \Nat the main SHINO'S restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.64,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you're the Magician of Legumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.64,sign_10813_142_Magician_of_Legu,Sign 0733,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Magician of {\c&H662DAB&}Legumes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:40.62,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I've still got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.08,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's open up some wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:43.86,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.60,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we barely within budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.69,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,This is my cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.07,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go to waste \Nif we don't pair it with wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.57,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.17,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, bring better wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.20,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.16,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,After making something this good,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.93,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,he still thinks it's not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.66,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.96,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,You will get closer to your own specialty \Nover the course of this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:10.30,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you can keep up with \Nthe work I require until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.08,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared, Monsieur Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:18.01,sign_11859_159_The_Next_Day__On,Sign 0816,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}The Next Day: Day 1 of the Pre-Open
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.78,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you better than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, better than you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.90,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,The chef's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.61,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought\N I'd get a laugh out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.61,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.98,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for the pre-open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.06,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:32.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.99,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's the difference between \Nthe pre-open and the actual open?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.09,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:43.98,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's a practice run \Nbefore the official open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.25,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,You invite mostly people you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:50.52,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,and check how well the staff are working \Ntogether while serving guests food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.72,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.99,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's partly to test\N the new menu of SHINO'S Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.76,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be changing dishes every day \Nwhile checking how the guests respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.71,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,On the final day of the pre-open,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:04.27,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,we'll even do a competition between \Nthe staff members for new menu items.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,A competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.39,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.15,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,You're done with your assigned tasks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.61,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I peeled everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.92,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and made lobster bouillon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:15.45,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've also already marinated octopus \Nand daikon root for half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:20.58,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Yukihira, \Nyou'll be my assistant for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.51,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get used to the work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.70,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,you might also become Abel-san's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.62,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:29.29,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,In the pre-open, three courses \Nwill be available for order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.85,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the course,\N a different main dish is served,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.76,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,or more amuses-bouches are served.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:39.19,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way, it's easy when you know \Nevery dish that needs to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.60,Main Dialogue,Guest,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-san, it's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.96,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.02,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.27,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The first customer has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.15,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I should get in position—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.15,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this sudden tension?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.03,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch over me, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.45,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,The customer has been seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.66,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.79,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oui, Chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.50,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So fast! Yet so quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.87,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can only hear the sound of knives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.38,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and the simmering of the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.51,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any unnecessary noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.26,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Next time that happens, \NI'll be kicking you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.38,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.01,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's so you don't miss \Nany minute change in sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.60,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Table 1's amuse-bouche is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.31,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.02,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from any other \Nkitchen I've experienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.77,Main Dialogue,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,So delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.36,Main Dialogue,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as good as its reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.83,Main Dialogue,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,He's indeed a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.85,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,The hors d'oeuvres are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.59,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.96,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,For Table 2 next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.59,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Four guests for Table 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders for Table 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.81,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, don't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.80,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly strain that fumet de poisson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.69,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.01,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The workload is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:10.69,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Even single prep work task has double the \Nnumber of steps there'd be for a diner dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.84,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, even while \Nwe're making appetizers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.77,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,we also have to start preparing the \Ntime-consuming main dishes at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.23,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, langoustine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:20.45,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Er, langoustines are... Norway lobsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.07,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.03,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Also, prepare a mirepoix ready to go \Nby around the time Table 3 finishes eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.42,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mirepoix...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.93,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Diced aromatic vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.71,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. I'm deciding so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:32.13,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I can manage to keep up, just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:34.22,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Table 3 just got their appetizer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.88,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,so I need to start with \Nprepping the fish for Table 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.53,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.60,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the mirepoix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.45,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Table 3's already finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.05,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.26,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's not ready yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.89,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,In a course menu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.57,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,it's an ironclad rule to serve the next dish \Nonly after everyone at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.46,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,has finished their current dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.32,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You have to match the pace of the guests
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.40,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and adjust when you'll serve the next dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.99,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There are multiple tables,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.82,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and they all arrived at different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.90,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you rush to prep for one table,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.41,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,a different table will sneak up on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:07.12,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, start prepping \Nthe mirepoix right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.60,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Lucie, delay Table 3's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.33,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare Table 1's fish first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:11.96,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:15.29,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Wei, Table 3's meat dish \Nwill be delayed five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.54,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Go explain to the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.21,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:20.51,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Abel, clean up after Yukihira's mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.63,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Oui, Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.93,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assist Table 1's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.51,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.29,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of helping Abel-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:28.56,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I held him up instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.06,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, if I've fallen behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.98,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've just had to worry about \Ncatching up on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.65,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But here, if I fall behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:39.36,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll affect everyone involved \Nin preparing the course menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.93,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.74,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't accepted you as one of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.49,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Abel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.82,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,What, you disagree?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.62,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need anyone who'll \Nslow down the kitchen's workflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.01,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the head chef of SHINO'S Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.75,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I have a responsibility to manage the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.24,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.75,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you're just part of the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.84,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get arrogant and think you've \Nmade your way into the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.32,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you get it, know your place—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.64,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The pre-open lasts five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.38,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.77,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:16.71,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a core member \Nby the last day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.47,Main Dialogue,Store,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are the ingredients?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.23,Main Dialogue,Store,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:06.82,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.79,Main Dialogue,Store,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:09.59,Main Dialogue,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.49,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.51,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.58,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,You can use the staff shower \Nanytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.21,sign_20514_297_Keep_Out,Sign 1418,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.21,Main Dialogue,Able,0000,0000,0000,,The kitchen staff usually arrive around noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.84,Main Dialogue,Able,0000,0000,0000,,so take care of personal matters until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.25,Main Dialogue,Able,0000,0000,0000,,Don't oversleep, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.25,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Based on how you worked today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.17,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be better if you didn't stay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:32.72,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,My success in Japan depends on the pre-open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.17,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,You may not feel the pressure, \Nbeing a student and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.23,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.92,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to bring in more \Ncustomers starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.94,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,The workload will increase \Ntwo or three-fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:50.05,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you change, you won't \Nbe here by the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.44,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Chef Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.04,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to give him any advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.68,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the time to hold his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.66,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.28,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.32,Flashback Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, don't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.47,Flashback Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly strain that fumet de poisson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.85,Flashback Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.29,Flashback Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,This recette requires \Nthe ingredients to be julienned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:14.85,Flashback Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Redo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.06,Flashback Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,If you do it again, I'll kick you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.85,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is it delicious, or disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:22.98,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.84,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.95,sign_22257_324_Hayama_Akira___Y,Sign 1529,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama Akira \N Yukihira Soma \N Kurokiba Ryo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.16,sign_22395_325_43rd_Fall_Electi,Sign 1534,0000,0000,0000,,43rd Autumn Election Main Tournament \N{\fs32}Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:35.74,sign_22422_326_Hayama_Akira,Sign 1535,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}Hayama Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.08,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,My own...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.50,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,...unique...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.26,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,...cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:56.26,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There are three possible ways to cut the \Npotatoes that are served with this recette:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,pont neuf, allumette, and paille.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.56,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The thickness and the length \Nof each type differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,As for how to cut fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,there's médaillon, darne, \Ntronçon, and escalope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.92,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have to differentiate between them \Nbased on the ingredients and the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:13.03,sign_23247_336_Day_2_of_the_Pre,Sign 1610,0000,0000,0000,,Day 2 of the Pre-Open
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.03,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Abel-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.45,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Lucie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.59,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.78,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,You're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.50,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:27.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so I had questions about how to cut \Ningredients, the ones I messed up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.99,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you for your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.21,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,We have to clean and prep ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:36.22,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve asking \Nafter holding us back yesterday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:40.00,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant can't waste any more on you—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.00,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Abel-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:49.28,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,The cleaning and peeling... \Neverything's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.68,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Lucie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.67,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Answer Yukihira's questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.82,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.45,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know, Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about the different cutting techniques...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.75,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I get that médaillon and darne \Nbasically look like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.75,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,He did all this work by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but do tronçon and escalope \Nbasically look like this and that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.71,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Did he even get any sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.17,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, well tronçon is like this. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.13,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:17.72,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Redo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.22,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,You have 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.60,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll get right to it \Nafter I'm done with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.94,sign_23247_336_Day_2_of_the_Pre,Sign 1734,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Day 3 of the Pre-Open
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.42,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that kind of like an hors d'oeuvre?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.91,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll make it an entree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.37,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow! Faster next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.08,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.47,sign_23247_336_Day_2_of_the_Pre,Sign 1801,0000,0000,0000,,Day 4 of the Pre-Open
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.47,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.22,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,This is three days in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm really sorry \Nto bother you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:11.23,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, today I have about fifty questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:13.48,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.32,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.16,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you did it just like I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.28,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There are about three things \NI want to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.15,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.74,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:21.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}First off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.58,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,How can he stay so indifferent
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.58,Flashback Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So my way is fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.29,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,after being berated day after day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.57,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can figure out the rest on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:31.46,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,He should be painfully \Naware of how useless he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:30.40,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.46,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he dejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.10,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, tomorrow is the last day \Nof our pre-open event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.06,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.57,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The fish for Table 8, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The prep work's all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.23,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Merci!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finished with prepping the scorpionfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Please check!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.70,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finished with deglazing the suc!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finished with making champignon tourné!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.07,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing with mincing shallots! \NPlease check!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.25,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.12,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, Table 6's next!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:11.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.72,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have even a second \Nto feel sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:20.26,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm having way too much fun \Nmastering new techniques!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.64,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,He's absorbing it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.89,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,With incredible force and speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.00,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Table 4's quickly working \Nthrough their course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.11,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can we hurry up their soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.94,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.32,Italics Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done with the prep work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.21,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Abel, can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.06,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:40.26,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,I can't right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.53,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.28,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The prep work's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.22,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.87,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,You've memorized the recette, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.83,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Finish the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:54.75,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.19,Main Dialogue Top,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was the best food \NI've ever tasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.49,Main Dialogue,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could check it out \Nduring the pre-open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.26,Main Dialogue Top,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to bring a few friends next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.22,Main Dialogue,Guests,0000,0000,0000,,Once it opens, we won't be \Nable to make a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.76,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,The pre-open ends tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.31,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slack on the last day, Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.56,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.45,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:17.94,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Abel, do you object to \Nkeeping Yukihira around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.22,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:23.18,Main Dialogue,Abel,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose he gets \Npassing marks right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.27,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,I was really worried for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.35,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't give him any advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.19,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point if he can't \Nfigure it out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.37,Italics Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.70,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-senpai, I'm sorry to bother you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.01,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I have one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.63,Flashback Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Monsieur Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.05,Flashback Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have another complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:44.76,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Does that Totsuki rule apply to alumni, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.64,Flashback Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:48.51,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shokugeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.58,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,If I beat you in a Shokugeki,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.31,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,will you rescind Tadokoro's expulsion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.28,Italics Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,You challenged me, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.78,Italics Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't fail at something \Nlike the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.67,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:16.79,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.09,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.13,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.47,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.43,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,What, Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.28,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:30.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:34.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Since it looks like I'm allowed to stay \Nuntil the last day, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:36.48,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:38.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.46,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be a new menu item competition \Nafter the restaurant closes tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want to submit a dish, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:46.57,Main Dialogue,Wei,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.61,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,The competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.41,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,But you've had your hands full assisting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:52.68,Main Dialogue,Lucie,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:56.30,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I always planned on \Nparticipating in the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:22:01.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make everything I've envisioned \Nuntil now into a reality as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.58,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be anything decent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:09.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.43,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it'll be the first time \NI'll have tasted an original recette of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:13.89,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.52,Main Dialogue,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
